1
00:00:00,520 --> 00:00:02,080
Life is complicated.

2
00:00:02,640 --> 00:00:05,640
I.. I never thought I'd live like this.

3
00:00:06,120 --> 00:00:06,360
No?

4
00:00:08,630 --> 00:00:10,770
When the war came, I did bad things.

5
00:00:11,150 --> 00:00:12,770
And after the war, I thought nothing of

6
00:00:12,770 --> 00:00:13,770
doing bad things.

7
00:00:14,310 --> 00:00:18,110
I killed people, smuggled people, sold people.

8
00:00:19,070 --> 00:00:21,250
And you don't worry about your soul?

9
00:00:25,830 --> 00:00:28,810
After you walk into a village and you

10
00:00:28,810 --> 00:00:31,729
see 50 children, all sitting neatly in a

11
00:00:31,729 --> 00:00:34,990
row against the church wall, each with their

12
00:00:34,990 --> 00:00:38,610
throats cut and their hands chopped off, you

13
00:00:38,610 --> 00:00:40,670
realize that the creature that could do this

14
00:00:41,310 --> 00:00:42,470
doesn't have a soul.

15
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:46,700
God is very complicated.

16
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:49,040
You mustn't give up hope.

17
00:00:49,380 --> 00:00:51,840
Well, I don't know about that.

